data.value: CREATE TABLE "TargetSystem"( "SystemID" IDENTITY DEFAULT '0', "SystemName" VARCHAR(70), "Description" VARCHAR(255), "TransferTypeID" INTEGER, "SourceDir" VARCHAR(255), "TargetServer" VARCHAR(50), "TargetDir" VARCHAR(255), "ProcessID" VARCHAR(20), "PrimaryNodeName" VARCHAR(50), "SecondaryNodeName" VARCHAR(50), "LoginInput" VARCHAR(50), "PasswordInput" VARCHAR(50), "PostScript" VARCHAR(255), "CreatedBy" VARCHAR(10), "CreatedDate" DATETIME, "ModifiedBy" VARCHAR(10), "ModifiedDate" DATETIME, PRIMARY KEY ("SystemID") )
